## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date sources and the scope of the search, which focused primarily on online resources. Some sources may not provide a comprehensive view of the topic, and the lack of specific publication dates for some articles could affect the currency of the information. Additionally, the report does not extensively cover the negative aspects of industrialization, which could provide a more balanced perspective.